                            <comment id="13106711" author="jbellis" created="Fri, 16 Sep 2011 19:02:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Maybe we should just extend the existing IOException to Exception.  Basically our attitude should be &quot;I don&apos;t care what went wrong loading the cache, it&apos;s optional, let me continue.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13108024" author="eldondev" created="Mon, 19 Sep 2011 17:48:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sounds good to me.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13112911" author="jbellis" created="Thu, 22 Sep 2011 21:09:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;committed, thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13112966" author="hudson" created="Thu, 22 Sep 2011 22:22:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in Cassandra-0.8 #337 (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://builds.apache.org/job/Cassandra-0.8/337/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://builds.apache.org/job/Cassandra-0.8/337/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
